<![CDATA[<a href="https://instagram.com/p/DE3PvUcSL1i/">View on Instagram</a><p><img src="https://scontent-bos5-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/474011767_18368414047187447_5492467038690856936_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh0.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-bos5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=1&_nc_ohc=vFd7j2YXIw4Q7kNvgGYc9JF&_nc_gid=c076fce5cf474a22a5d9ebe6c10e539c&edm=AGenrX8BAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AYBXcF-pFEOWXh_R6KMwKffwta4xBn-LpJN7tx5mGNgsUQ&oe=67B3C0B8&_nc_sid=ed990e" /><br>First responders are the best people on earth… thank you for what you do. it’s been an honour meeting you guys. 🚨 #lastrong If you have a following: Do fucking better, influence people for the better. It’s not just about you.. it’s bigger than you. #california #californialove #firstresponders #palisade #malibu #firefighter #firefighters #lawenforcement #lafires #californiafires #influncer #giveback #dobetter #burgers]]>
