<item>
<title><![CDATA[I’m incredibly grateful for being able to do what I do, and wo...]]></title>
<link>https://imginn.com/p/DExqUjJR6-o/</link>
<guid>https://imginn.com/p/DExqUjJR6-o/</guid>
<description>
<![CDATA[<a href="https://instagram.com/p/DExqUjJR6-o/">View on Instagram</a><p><img src="https://scontent-bos5-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/473660624_18368131453187447_7969770754897324120_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh0.08_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-bos5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=111&_nc_ohc=ZW6-I1ymvrYQ7kNvgHp_gNU&_nc_gid=18c605bf335b463bae905ec0df375e53&edm=AGenrX8BAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AYDiI3FNohltR55sfYas-qcJ5SgbZXkYmIZsBrBrA1Y57A&oe=67B3AF88&_nc_sid=ed990e" /><br>I’m incredibly grateful for being able to do what I do, and wouldn’t possible without you guys watching my videos, I’m even more grateful for every first responder and person working tirelessly to fight these fires. 🚨👮🏼‍♂️🧑🏼‍🚒It’s not just about handing out burgers or a meal, but about showing up and putting a fucking smile on these heroes’ faces, even if it’s just for a minute. They’re giving everything to protect our community. TO OTHER CONTENT CREATORS AND PEOPLE WITH A FOLLOWING: if you aren’t posting about what’s going on in your communities, and only pushing your content or products.. you should be fucking embarrassed. Step up…. Don’t just sit back and post about meaningless shit. #california #californiafires #palisades #malibu #wildfires #firstresponders #firefighter #firefighters #losangeles #lafires]]>
</description>
<pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 06:15:46 -0500</pubDate>
</item>
<item>
<title><![CDATA[To all the first responders fighting these fires—some of you h...]]></title>
<link>https://imginn.com/p/DEsjvmSSgaS/</link>
<guid>https://imginn.com/p/DEsjvmSSgaS/</guid>
<description>
<![CDATA[<a href="https://instagram.com/p/DEsjvmSSgaS/">View on Instagram</a><p><img src="https://scontent-bos5-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/473615172_18367855096187447_2636402945798713358_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-bos5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=111&_nc_ohc=iRWAha_kptMQ7kNvgEr27CK&_nc_gid=9bc5501d0d8f47438358590d7357e978&edm=AGenrX8BAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AYD9CakEEp-yQw_L7K8vVc0LPgWoFbdZ0qvI51LOUeYc4g&oe=67B3AE2B&_nc_sid=ed990e" /><br>To all the first responders fighting these fires—some of you haven’t fucking slept in days, yet you still show up, exhausted, relentless and working around the clock.You’re not out here for the “thanks” but you fucking deserve it. Thank you for all that you do. First responders are some of the most selfless people I’ve met in my fucking life.👮🏼‍♂️🧑🏼‍🚒🚨 To anyone that has a platform, a voice, a following: Stop posting only about yourself. If you’ve got a platform, use it to actually help. Fuck the vanity—do better, raise awareness, and show up for something bigger than you. This is all bigger than social media, build a better community, build something special. Whatever you see on social media about these fires, it’s worse in person. I’m not saying that to be pessimistic, it’s just the reality. If you can help, there’s a link in my bio. If you can’t help, that’s okay. But if you can, do it. #california #californiafires #firefighters #firefighter #firstresponders #malibu #eatoncanyon #altadena #palisades #losangeles #wildfires #sunsetblvd #hollywood]]>
</description>
<pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 06:15:47 -0500</pubDate>
</item>
